ounces since 1986 although british drug experts say this might not 
include small amounts seized 
cocaine seizures on the other hand rose from 345 pounds in 1978 
to almost six tons last year in europe exceeding the heroin haul 
for the first time interpol says 
we were caught napping when heroin first arrived in the early 
70s says hans lundborg narcotics bureau chief at swedens 
ministry for social affairs the government cant afford to make 
that same mistake again 
