sugar futures prices fluctuated widely on new yorks coffee 
sugar amp cocoa exchange as traders bought into the market on news of 
a large purchase by india and bailed out on reports the european 
sugar beet crop may exceed last years 
adding to sugar price instabilty is what analysts say is the 
